# Random Tables

The best game prep can't anticipate everything. Players ask unexpected questions, pursue tangents, demand details you haven't prepared. Random tables transform improvisation panic into confident ad-lib creativity. Roll once, get immediate usable results—no lengthy consultation required.

These tables provide quick NPC generation, instant complications, and on-the-fly details that make improvised content feel prepared. Keep them behind your screen for when players zigg where you planned zagg.

